column2: SELECT TOP # p.objID, p.ra, p.dec, p.type, p.q_u, p.u_u, p.modelMag_u, p.modelMag_g, p.modelMag_r, p.modelMag_i, p.modelMag_z, s.specObjID, s.z, s.zErr, s.sourcetype, s.class, s.subClass, s.velDisp, s.velDispErr FROM #upload u JOIN #x x ON x.up_id = u.up_id JOIN PhotoTag p ON p.objID = x.objID JOIN SpecObjAll s ON p.objID = s.bestObjID ORDER by x.up_id
